Introduction

Jeong Saebi is a South Korean dancer and singer under WAKEONE.

In 2024, she was a contestant on Mnet' survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she ended up ranking 6th place in the final with 294,721 votes, but was chosen as the 7th member by the producers, thus securing her spot as a member of the final group, izna.

Jeong Saebi made her debut with the group on November 25, 2024, with the release of their first mini album titled "N/a".

On February 26, 2025, it was reported that she would be the new MC for SBS MTV's The Show alongside WayV's Xiaojun and CRAVITY's Hyeongjun. Her first broadcast was held on March 4, 2025.
